;Mercenary (Japanese<nowiki>:</nowiki> {{lj|傭兵}})
:CV: Tsuyoshi Koyama, Emiko Takeuchi(young)
:''A Beastfallen mercenary who protects Zero''
;Albus (Japanese<nowiki>:</nowiki> {{lj|アルバス}})
