=== Game ===
The magic command battle game '''''Grimoire of Zero''''' (Japanese: {{lj|ゼロから始める魔法の書}}) on iOS/Android is developed by NOW PRODUCTION and operated by GREE, it was released on May 23, 2017. The game requires over iOS 8.0 or over Android 4.3. 

{{Kakeru Kobashiri}}
